HEADWORD: Cyanometer
<hw>Cy`a*nom"e*ter</hw> <pr>(s?`?-n?m"?-t?r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[Gr. <grk>ky`anos</grk> a dark blue substance + <ets>-meter</ets>:
cf. F. <ets>cyanom⟦egrave⟧tre</ets>.]</ety> <def>An instrument for
measuring degrees of blueness.</def>⟦br⟧
